5607c1dc-5c93-4730-94bc-d6d2af85687b	1fd62ebf-812e-4e98-9240-ee4d3b7a0da6	日本から行きました。ここは最高のシャーマン、最高のもてなし、最高の体験が約束されたリトリート施設です。シャーマンのWinister、そして主催者のウィリアムは知性、見識ともに高く、愛に溢れた素晴らしい人達です。そしてウィリアムの家族総出のもてなしは親切心に溢れ、アヤワスカ体験に伴うあらゆる事態に対応してくれます。\n宿泊施設も清潔で、各部屋にシャワー、トイレがあり、Wifiや電気も通っています。\n私は4回のアヤワスカ儀式と最終日のサンペドロの儀式を体験しました。それは私の魂の浄化と、Unconditional Loveを学ぶ為の人生で最も重要な学びの場になりました。この施設に訪れることができて非常に嬉しく思います。激しくお勧めします。また来年も訪れたいと思います。	Ensako Norihide	5
141c3472-0144-41e1-ad25-3eaeb189afa9	1fd62ebf-812e-4e98-9240-ee4d3b7a0da6	The most impactful, important, loving, learning and beautiful part of my life and part of my journey. My loving father runs the retreat with the rest of my beautiful family. And the staff and workers are such beautiful and nice people I’ve ever met and taught me so many things! I haven’t seen my father since I was 11 years old and I came to visit him when I was 20 years old. 10 years without seeing my family and it was an amazing time with them! Aswell as the beautiful medicine of Ayahuasca and San Pedro, I never came to Peru seeking to do this but only to see my family but deciding to do it was amazing. It changed my life so much and gave me so much growth and much self love❤️. It helped me so much! I highly recommend taking a trip there if you want to experience a beautiful and loving time feeling like family and enjoying life, aswell as learning so much and healing!! God bless love you all!	Sosa Dom	5
126c1879-3c85-41eb-b0dd-2e49f146f8a7	1fd62ebf-812e-4e98-9240-ee4d3b7a0da6	The perfect place for my first Ayahausca experience, I wouldn't go anywhere else, it was like going home. I felt safe and was guided by authentic shamans who were able to help me on this life changing journey, so very grateful for them. Beautiful location and retreat centre. Lots of fun day activities. The facilitators and workers felt like family.	Kirby TheKirbstar Drew	5
