28219986-c210-4a98-a50a-5b02ff6bb699	cmp239xc5000fml2udurcav05	Spanish:\nMira que solo nos quedamos en este hotel por una nochecita antes de irnos a Machu Picchu y luego a Cusco, pero la atención y la belleza del lugar fueron espectaculares. La cena estuvo riquísima — la señorita Úrsula nos dio una atención de primera e hizo la noche muy agradable con su lindo humor y su amabilidad.\n\nNos quedamos en las habitaciones coloniales, que fueron muy, muy cómodas. Todo estaba limpiecito y de primera.\n\nEl desayuno fue excelente, y la atención de Gualberto también fue de primera, asegurándose de que nuestra experiencia fuera excelente. Al despedirnos, nos trajo un matecito de coca en un vaso desechable para podérnoslo llevar, y de verdad que estuvo riquísimo y calientito en el camino a la estación de tren.\n\nLa verdad es que la experiencia fue increíble, y sin duda nos quedaríamos en este hotel espectacular otra vez.\n\nEnglish:\n\nWe only stayed at this hotel for one night before heading to Machu Picchu and then Cusco, but the service and the beauty of the place were spectacular. Dinner was delicious — Miss Úrsula gave us top-notch service and made the evening very enjoyable with her sweet sense of humor and kindness.\n\nWe stayed in the colonial rooms, which were very, very comfortable. Everything was spotless and high quality.\n\nBreakfast was excellent, and Gualberto’s service was also top-notch, making sure our experience was great. When we were leaving, he brought us a little cup of coca tea in a disposable cup so we could take it with us, and it was honestly so good and nice and warm on the way to the train station.\n\nOverall, the experience was amazing, and we would absolutely stay at this wonderful hotel again.	Sebastian Martens	5
df1d7fc6-4de5-4a85-a170-906e3970a9ac	cmp239xc5000fml2udurcav05	Wonderful gem of a hotel in the midst of Sacred Valley. My wife & I had a wonderful 90 minutes massage by Yesica and Yudelina respectively.  The Spa’s front spa reception person (Ariatna) has been most helpful - she offered us some wonderful hot tea and let us rest at the comfortable waiting lounge beds for 25 mins while waiting for our massage session to start.  Highly recommend this 5-star spa as treatment especially before or after your Macchu Picchu climb👍	Paul Fong	5
