8f08950f-2aa8-4ad7-a87f-e926d764b560	cmp239xe0001aml2urydybhoo	A year and a half on between writing this original review below I feel continuously amazed in witnessing the innovation in what’s being offered to participants who choose to practice at Tantraya. I’m so happy to be part in this community that offers unique teachings in Pisac through the guidance of a teacher who I’ve experienced profoundly transformation shifts in the way I relate to consciousness and consciously interacting in this world that be here now. Loved the baugua and vipassana retreats! Really grateful for all that has been shared through these teachings, really feel right now like I’m just at the tip of the iceberg. So happy to learn and be part of learning through what’s being shared here it just keeps getting more exciting!\n\nBeing lead to Tantraya to learn and grow under a lineage and legend that comes together for the merit and benefit of all sentient beings has touched the soul deeply in contentment of a longing in fulfilment in the empty spaciousness of the vastly infinite gift of presence within being present within the here and now. The gift that be omnipresent forever available in all its splendour. Forever opening in blissful unconditional expansiveness. Surrendering and letting go into the freedom that lay within the liberated presence of feeling every moment in its fullest expression here and now.\n\nUnderstanding the interconnectivity between all that is, all that ever has been and all that ever will be in relationship to all that we be in witness of in this divinity has been a blessing in awakening to true responsibility in being part of humanity.\n\nFeeling into infinity, in love for humanity that there be spaces available for us to come together in harmony, working together in synchronicity, in shared intentionality for the merit and benefit of all that is, all that has ever been and all that will ever be.\n\nWith Gratitude,\n\nAdrian	Transcending Attachment	5
13282bad-c2f0-488d-9f90-5b863a08a40a	cmp239xe0001aml2urydybhoo	If you are looking for a life changing experience do yourself a favor and come to Tantraya. It’s a place unlike any other. Paul provides amazing practices and really does amazing work. He is dedicated to everyone who is dedicated to the work. Do your best to let go and surrender and the work you want done will happen for you. So important to be lead by someone who knows what they are doing and will provide a safe space for you to really let go. Paul does this and so much more. I let go of YEARS of sadness and watched it transform into love with Paul’s support my life has changed.\n\nSuper transformational, special, sacred, place. You will be transformed if you are willing to do the work, and you deserve it so take a chance on yourself and go to Tantrya! 🤗	M V	5
b611b0bc-d935-4aac-908f-00551d153e37	cmp239xe0001aml2urydybhoo	I’ve been part of Tantraya’s community for 2,5 years now. What a beautiful and transformative journey it has been and one that keeps continuously unfolding.\n\nTantraya is not just an Ayahuasca center although medicine plays an important role here, it’s much more than that… It’s a school that will teach you how to meet life fully, with trust, stability, and courage. Daily practices, medicine work, and a service-oriented attitude create a very stable container for getting in touch with our true nature by shedding what we’re not, and becoming what we’ve always been.\n\nPaul’s wisdom and skill level are just a different level. His deep experience in many different spiritual and shamanic traditions creates a very unique, powerful, and most importantly effective combination. Having a teacher who has walked the path before is priceless in these arts. So, if you’re reading it and feeling like you’re walking blindly and looking for a guide, search no more :)\n\nIf you’re looking for the highest quality ayahuasca ceremonies, magical training, healing modalities, and internal alchemy training - THIS IS THE PLACE.\n\nLastly, I’m feeling so grateful for all the students and participants of Tantraya’s retreats and courses who gratefully, I can call friends. It’s such a blessing to have the power of the sangha so present in one’s life. May you all be happy and free, thank you! <3	Michalina Sobków	5
28fc3604-1679-4c1e-be87-d9d455f323c9	cmp239xe0001aml2urydybhoo	I can only give 5 stars on google but if I’m honest not even all the stars in the universe could represent how much I recommend this place 💫\nTantraya is the most magickal and heavenly palace I’ve ever been to and the experience here is beyond human words, but I’ll try to write something anyway.\n\nWhen I had my first ceremony in January 2023 I had this deep inner knowing that this is the right place for me. I wasn’t fully conscious that I had been looking and longing for such a place but when I was here I knew. It felt like arriving, some sort of coming home.\n\nIt is the biggest blessing of my life to receive the teachings and especially by this monumental being of love called Paul. I’ve never met such a bright, full of light, compassionate, self-sacrificing human before. He IS unconditional love embodied in physical form. His presence, kindness and pure love melts my heart & every dark spot away and brings me back to the same state that is also within me and within all of us.\n\nPaul’s teachings are very unique as he has gained so much knowledge and wisdom from various traditions, e.g. Buddhism, Taoism, Shamanism, Magick, Sufism… and puts them together in a very holistic and special way.\nI do highly recommend the ayahuasca retreats in which he calls upon very high spiritual beings for support. Each retreat has a different specialization and brings its own individual cosmic spice.\n\nApart from this you have the extraordinary chance to deepen your knowledge even further by studying with him - in presence and/ or online. Traditional Chinese Medicine, Inner Martial arts, the western path of Magick - it is all possible here and it is the sweetest gift for those who feel the call to dive further and further.\n\nDoing the work here has changed and is changing me in a very profound way. I’m in deep gratitude for every single experience at Tantraya. Growth can be challenging and painful sometimes - but here you’re always safely guided, hold and protected.\nIf you feel the call to walk the spiral path, to fully let go and surrender into the divine, I dearly invite you to go there and meet this enchanting team & community.\n\nA little side note: as it is an ideal place to linger and immerse yourself fully in the teachings - bringing some time with you might be helpful 🧚\n\nIf anybody reading this has any question, feel free to reach out, I would be delighted to help you out.\n\nAnd finally, don’t forget or eat Kelley’s amazing gluten-free vegan muffins at retreat breakfast;)	Sina Waidmann	5
