7c37ac89-f7cb-4dab-8b08-e86fa4536473	cmp239xis003hml2u2386ti8t	I met Noemi on a pedestrian street in Cusco and later decided to visit her massage place. It’s located on the second floor of Centro Comercial Sotomayor. The space is clean, and the restroom is separate from the massage area. There are two comfortable massage beds, suitable for couples or friends. The environment is quiet and relaxing, and I felt comfortable during my visits. I’ve been there four times during my stay in Cusco and had a good experience each time. I would consider visiting again if I return.\n\n我在库斯科的一条步行街上遇到了诺埃米，后来决定去她那里做按摩。按摩店位于索托马约尔购物中心的二楼。店面干净整洁，洗手间与按摩区是分开的。店里有两张舒适的按摩床，适合情侣或朋友一起。环境安静放松，每次去都感觉很舒服。我在库斯科期间一共去了四次，每次体验都很好。如果再去库斯科，我还会考虑去那里。	siwei Zhong	5
