484fd58e-b2f0-4be1-a8bd-a851da86cf68	cmp239xih003cml2unl0ezc74	We booked three rooms in total. The matrimonial room (5) was spacious and well-equipped, with a heater, fridge, and wardrobe. In the second building, the twin room (7) was also relatively spacious and had a heater, making it more comfortable than the twin room (3), which felt quite cramped. In room (3), there was hardly any space to store clothes or bags, so we had to place everything on the bed.\n\nThe bathroom was small but had good water pressure for the shower, and soap, shampoo, and conditioner were provided. However, no complimentary drinking water bottles were available.\n\nBreakfast box was enough as we left at 4AM.	Ilyi	3
