a7f26658-4e6d-4c6d-a71c-004b033d1c00	cmp1pode0000lml2i1hcocf2m	This performance is included in the Cusco Tourist Ticket and many of the tour guides recommend you see this show. Arrive an hour early to get good seats.\n\nThe performers are costumed in cultural wear while dancing and singing local and traditional pieces, though they are not using microphones so the sound quality can be uneven. Production values are on par for a local community show.\n\nOverall the show provides a good introduction of the traditíonal dances and costumes of the Cusco region.\n\nAs a bonus, you can also occasionally find groups in front of the Cusco Cathedral at the Plaza de Armas practicing traditional dances, though not usually in costume.	Gary Chow	3
