dc8986c5-41ba-47c1-8ac3-715344c0bbed	cmp1q4voa0020ml2id3y9pdy4	As a retreat host, this space was the perfect size! We wanted intimate, sweet, beautiful , special and powerful! It is exactly what we needed and wanted. Jyl made it so easy for planning , expeditions, shuttle , communication and making this boutique retreat center meet our needs. The grounds- immaculate! The rooms-spacious and curated with little Peruvian boutique touches. The food- beyond our expectations and encouraged me to do better once home! The flowers- the nature- the yoga space- the double rainbows (Jyl didn’t have the control on this one but Apu was blessing us with vibrancy and blessings). I can’t wait to return, hear the river out our window and feel the power of this space and the mountains once again.	Camie Garvey	5
