9fc370b8-7a23-4f6d-9d71-d4a5dbf0f098	cmp207bk3000lmlpos6e9yv02	I wholeheartedly recommend the Sapan Inka Ayahuasca Retreat Center. From my very first email exchanges, I was reassured by the professionalism, warmth, and clarity of Erik and Nilda. This was my first experience with Ayahuasca, and it turned out to be one of the most profound and transformative experiences of my life.\nThroughout the ceremony, I felt deeply cared for, thanks to Erik’s genuine attention to each participant. His presence created a safe and supportive environment, allowing me to open fully to the Ayahuasca experience while always feeling secure and grounded.\nWhat impressed me most is Erik’s rare ability to build a bridge between the Western scientific mindset and the wisdom of ancient shamanic traditions. This balance brought an added depth and trust to the process.\nI sincerely hope to return to Sapan Inka and to Erik and Nilda soon, to continue this journey of healing and discovery.	N B	5
