dd5590a8-f9f7-48f3-9c4f-7769b56caf97	cmp1thzmx00a8ml2i97ps6sa8	Staying at Ayllu BnB was one of the most special parts of my trip. From the very beginning, Antonio and Nicole made me feel like family. They were both so kind, quick to respond, and always willing to help with anything I needed. Antonio even stepped in last minute to help me with booking a tour guide, which I was so grateful for, and Nicole was the sweetest, always checking in and making sure I was comfortable.\n\nThe house itself is beautiful, with the most breathtaking views from the terrace, the dining room, and even my room. Waking up to that scenery every day felt like such a gift. They made me a fresh delicious breakfast or packed me a lunch everyday. The value with this spot is amazing. The rooms were clean and comfortable. I was there 6 nights and every single day was in awe of the beauty.\n\nI also can’t forget their adorable dog Charlotte. She completely stole my heart. She was so cute and playful, and just having her around made my days even brighter.\nThis place is full of warmth and heart, and I honestly can’t wait for the chance to come back	linnette dones	5
