be318020-d355-4420-80d4-1d60efd80d6b	cmp4hcce5000zmlqqacreey6u	Ate here during my tour. A really great place with very professional service. They served really great food and I really liked the lomo saltado. Lomo saltado is the beef steak dish, served with rice and french fries. The beef was very tender and the sauce was great. Overall, a nice place to stop for a while and have lunch before continuing your journey exploring the beauty of Peru!	Google Reviewer	5
